::Prowl/Zeus::

Prowl nods, letting go of Zeus and sending the newcomer smashing into the 
ground. He lands near Shadow Wing, looking at the unconscious eagle.

"I'm fine. Let's get back to buisness," he says, turning to fire at Ares.
